        <Parent_String>light-sensitive reprographic processes [300246172], reprographic processes [300240132], copying [300053257], image-making processes and techniques [300053159], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
